text: And thou shalt feast before the Lord thy God, Thou, and thy Son, and thy Daughter, and thy Manservant, and the Levite that is within thy gates, and the Stranger, and the Fatherless, and the Widow, who abide with you, in the place which the Lord thy God shall choose, that his name may dwell there, there shall choose, that his name doth.
